</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,1403,942,968]" pageId="19" pageNumber="546" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,150,968]" box="[199,1403,942,968]" pageId="19" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,942,968]" pageId="19" pageNumber="546">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after its blackish-brown hind femur: 
<emphasis box="[840,899,943,968]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="546">niger</emphasis>
is Latin for black, 
<emphasis box="[1112,1191,942,968]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="546">femora</emphasis>
is Latin for femur.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
